Hi, sawadazina
  do you solved this bug, i have the same bug in android mobile

It is recommended that you use navigator to switch between the Android side. Since a single js file represents an active activity window on the Android side, the vue-router mode switch is to refresh the current window, so there will be flashing, and the page missing problem is not there. Solve, hope to help you a little
